description: The sweet folks of Santa Rosa know that NitroKarma is the way to go when it comes to the most delicious liquid-nitro frozen ice cream. All fresh, all homemade, all frozen right before your eyes! You’ll find their flavors like Butter Pecan, Chocolate Chip Espresso Walnut, and Pumpkin Pie to be so deliciously clever that you'll agree that this is the best ice cream ever.So be sure to awe your guests at your next event with ice cream that is simply the best, courtesy of NitroKarma.
name: NitroKarma
